### Basic Textarea Field in Payload Collection (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/textarea.mdx

This example demonstrates a minimal configuration for a Textarea Field within a Payload CMS collection. It defines a 'metaDescription' field of type 'textarea' and marks it as 'required'. This is a fundamental setup for using textarea inputs.

```typescript
import type { CollectionConfig } from 'payload'

export const ExampleCollection: CollectionConfig = {
  slug: 'example-collection',
  fields: [
    {
      name: 'metaDescription', // required
      type: 'textarea', // required
      required: true,
    },
  ],
}
```

