### Custom Textarea Field Client Component (React/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/textarea.mdx

This example provides a custom client component for a Textarea Field using React and TypeScript, marked with 'use client'. It imports the TextareaField from '@payloadcms/ui' and renders it with all passed props. This component is responsible for the interactive behavior of the textarea in the browser.

```tsx
'use client'
import React from 'react'
import { TextareaField } from '@payloadcms/ui'
import type { TextareaFieldClientComponent } from 'payload'

export const CustomTextareaFieldClient: TextareaFieldClientComponent = (
  props,
) => {
  return <TextareaField {...props} />
}
```

